za|J\u00falio C\u00e9sar]]\n*{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Alessandro Soares|Soares]]\n*{{flagicon|SER}} [[Vladimir Ivi\u0107]]\n*{{flagicon|SER}} [[Nikola Malba\u0161a]]\n|}\n\n===International players===\n{|\n|- style='vertical-align:top'\n||\n*{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Georgios Alexopoulos|Giorgos Alexopoulos]]\n*{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Dionisis Chiotis]]\n*{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Traianos Dellas]]\n*{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Kostas Katsouranis]]\n*{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Vassilis Lakis]]\n||\n*{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Nikos Liberopoulos]]\n*{{flagicon|SER}} [[Vladimir Ivi\u0107]]\n*{{flagicon|SER}} [[Nikola Malba\u0161a]]\n*{{flagicon|UKR}} [[Oleh Venglinsky]]\n||\n|}\n\n<gallery>\n File:Stefano Sorrentino.JPG|[[Stefano Sorrentino]] (2012)\n File:Louay Chanko.jpg|[[Louay Chanko]] (2010)\n File:Sokratis Papastathopoulos Greece.jpg|[[Sokratis Papastathopoulos]] (2010-11-17)\n File:Panagiotis Kone.jpg|[[Panagiotis Kone]] (2010)\n File:Bruno Cirillo 2.jpg|[[Bruno Cirillo]] (2008)\n File:Pantelis Kapetanos.PNG|[[Pantelis Kapetanos]] (2010)\n</gallery>\n\n===Squad changes (Summer 2005)===\n\n'''In:'''\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no=1|nat=Italy|pos=GK|name=[[Stefano Sorrentino]]|other=on loan from [[Torino F.C.|Torino]] for \u20ac100K}}\n{{Fs player|no=5|nat=Italy|pos=DF|name=[[Bruno Cirillo]]|other=from [[U.S. Lecce]] for free}}\n{{Fs player|no=6|nat=Greece|pos=DF|name=[[Georgios Alexopoulos|Giorgos Alexopoulos]]|other=from [[Egaleo F.C.|Egaleo]] for free}}\n{{Fs player|no=7|nat=Brazil|pos=FW|name=[[Alessandro Soares|Soares]]|other=from [[OFI Crete|OFI]] for \u20ac150K}}\n{{Fs player|no=8|nat=Greece|pos=MF|name=[[Miltiadis Sapanis|Miltos Sapanis]]|other=from [[Panathinaikos FC|Panathinaikos]] for free}}\n{{Fs player|no=9|nat=Greece|pos=FW|name=[[Aggelos Komvolidis|Angelos Komvolidis]]|other=from [[VfB Stuttgart|VfB Stuttgart U-19]] for free}}\n{{Fs player|no=10|nat=Greece|pos=MF|name=[[Panagiotis Kone]]|other=promoted from [[AEK Athens F.C.|AEK Athens U-19]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=11|nat=Ukraine|pos=FW|name=[[Oleh Veng