=30|nat=Cyprus|pos=MF|name=[[Simos Krassas]]|other=on loan to [[Panionios F.C.|Panionios]] for 75K}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\nTotal income: {{gain}} \u20ac75K\n\n==Squad stats==\n{{Efs start|[[Alpha Ethniki 2005-06|Alpha Ethniki]]|[[Greek Cup 2005-06|Greek Cup]]|[[UEFA Cup 2005\u201306|UEFA Cup]]}}\n{{Efs player|no=1|nat=Greece|pos=GK|name=[[Dionisis Chiotis]]|25|0|3|0|2|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=3|nat=Serbia|pos=DF|name=[[Nikola Malba\u0161a]]|16|0|3|0|2|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=5|nat=Italy|pos=DF|name=[[Bruno Cirillo]]|24|2|2|1|2|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=6|nat=Greece|pos=DF|name=[[Georgios Alexopoulos|Giorgos Alexopoulos]]|30|3|3|0|2|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=7|nat=Brazil|pos=FW|name=[[Alessandro Soares|Soares]]|28|2|8|2|2|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=8|nat=Greece|pos=MF|name=[[Miltiadis Sapanis|Miltos Sapanis]]|11|0|3|1|0|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=9|nat=Greece|pos=FW|name=[[Aggelos Komvolidis|Angelos Komvolidis]]|0|0|0|0|0|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=10|nat=Greece|pos=MF|name=[[Panagiotis Kone]]|0|0|1|0|0|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=11|nat=Ukraine|pos=FW|name=[[Oleh Venglinsky]]|15|3|4|0|2|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=12|nat=Greece|pos=GK|name=[[Giannis Arabatzis]]|0|0|0|0|0|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=14|nat=Greece|pos=DF|name=[[Stavros Tziortziopoulos]]|9|0|4|0|0|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=15|nat=Greece|pos=DF|name=''[[Sokratis Papastathopoulos]]''|0|0|2|1|0|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=17|nat=Serbia|pos=MF|name=[[Vladimir Ivi\u0107]]|27|3|5|0|2|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=18|nat=Greece|pos=DF|name=[[Vaggelis Moras|Vangelis Moras]]|13|0|6|2|1|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=19|nat=Greece|pos=DF|name=[[Dimitris Koutromanos]]|0|0|1|0|0|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=20|nat=Greece|pos=MF|name=[[Vassilios Pliatsikas|Vasilis Pliatsikas]]|3|0|4|0|0|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=21|nat=Greece|pos=MF|name=[[Kostas Katsouranis]]|29|6|4|1|2|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=22|nat=Italy|pos=GK|name=[[Stefano Sorrentino]]|5|0|5|0|0|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=23|nat=Greece|pos=MF|name=[[Vassilis Lakis|Vasilis Lakis]]|28|4|5|0|1|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=24|nat=Greece|pos=DF|name=[[Christos Kontis]]|15|0|4|0|2|0}}\n